commit.message: Fixes #21 - Added support for line continuators in JavaScript literals.
Fixes #20 - Added support for line continuators in CSS strings.
Fixes #20 - Set JPMS automatic module name
Updated Maven plugins to latest versions
Fixes #19 - Set compilation baseline to Java 6
Added class org.unbescape.Unbescape in order to report the version of the library being used
Fixes #12 - Implemented a specific set of escaping methods for XML attribute values, always escaping \t, \n and \r.
Fixes #16 - Bad recognition of partial matches in NCRs with ommittable semicolon suffix
Fixes #14 - Add ampersand to level-1 escaping for JSON, JavaScript and CSS literals.
